metadata.description:
BFF helps women and nonbinary friends get educated, connected and rewarded in all things crypto.

Nearly 100 female and nonbinary leaders across crypto, tech, design, business, and many other industries have come together to help start and support the BFF community. These bracelets signify their status as a founding member. Together, we hope to foster the next generation of friends who crypto.

[mybff.xyz](https://www.mybff.xyz/)
metadata.name: Founding BFF Friendship Bracelets
